sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 📱 User
    participant Telco as 📡 Telco
    participant Gateway as 🌐 USSD Gateway
    participant Django as ⚙️ Django
    participant Engine as 🔄 UssdEngine
    participant YAML as 📄 YAML Journey
    participant Utils as 🐍 utils.py
    participant Redis as 🗄️ Redis
    participant DB as 💾 Database

    User->>Telco: Dials *123#
    Telco->>Gateway: USSD session start
    Gateway->>Django: POST /dental_ussd/dental_ussd_gw/<br/>{sessionId, phoneNumber, MSG, serviceCode}
    Django->>Django: _validate_request()<br/>parse MSG, build CustomUssdRequest
    Django->>Engine: UssdEngine(ussd_request).ussd_dispatcher()
    Engine->>Redis: load session data
    Redis-->>Engine: session dict
    Engine->>YAML: get_screens(initial_screen)
    YAML-->>Engine: screen definition
    alt function_screen
        Engine->>Utils: call utils.function(ussd_request)
        Utils->>DB: ORM query
        DB-->>Utils: result
        Utils-->>Engine: return value
        Engine->>Redis: session[session_key] = return_value
    else router_screen
        Engine->>Engine: evaluate Jinja2 expression<br/>against session data
        Engine->>YAML: get_screens(next_screen)
    else menu_screen / input_screen
        Engine-->>Django: UssdResponse(text, status=True)
        Django-->>Gateway: {status: success, MSG: "...", MSGTYPE: CON}
        Gateway-->>Telco: Show menu
        Telco-->>User: Display on phone
    else quit_screen
        Engine-->>Django: UssdResponse(text, status=False)
        Django-->>Gateway: {status: success, MSG: "...", MSGTYPE: END}
        Gateway-->>Telco: End session
        Telco-->>User: Display final message
    end
